Dele Odule (a mụrụ na Nọvemba 23, 1961) bụ onye na-eme ejije na onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri na Naijiria. A họpụtara ya na "Best Supporting Actor (Yoruba) n'afọ 2014 Best of Nollywood Awards maka ọrụ ya na ihe nkiri Kori Koto Ọ na-eje ozi ugbu a dịka onye isi oche nke Theatre Arts and Movie Practitioners Association of Nigeria

A mụrụ Odule n'obodo Ile-Ife, Osun Steeti, mana ọ bụ onye Oru Ijebu, na Ijebu North local government dị na Ogun Steeti n'afọ 1961, ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ sekọndrị. O nwere asambodo Grade II site na Teacher's Training College, Oru tupu ọ gaa Mahadum nke Ibadan, Oyo Steeti ebe ọ gụrụ Theatre Arts.
Dele malitere ime ejije na otu ihe nkiri a na-akpọ Oloko Theatre Group n'okpuru nduzi nke Mukaila Adebisi
Ọ pụtara nke mbụ ya n'afọ 1986 tupu ọ pụta nnukwu n'ihe ngosi mgbe ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri akpọrọ Ti Oluwa Ni Ile Kemgbe ahụ, ọ gara n'ihu na-eme ihe nkiri karịrị narị abụọ.
